@startuml Regenerative Producers Exclusive Access
title **Access Policy: Regenerative Producers Only**\nSensitive practices data shared exclusively among certified producers

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #424242
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #9E9E9E
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam noteBorderColor #F9A825
skinparam sequenceGroupBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #2E7D32

actor "Sarah Chen\n(White Buffalo Land Trust)\n//regenerative-verified//" as Sarah #E8F5E9
actor "Dr. Martinez\n(Point Blue)\n//researcher//" as Martinez #E3F2FD
actor "Corporate Analyst\n//corporate//" as Corp #FFF3E0

participant "Caney Fork\nEDC Connector" as CF_EDC #E8F5E9

note over CF_EDC
  Caney Fork publishes a **proprietary
  grazing protocol** dataset with the
  **regenerative-producers** access policy.

  This contains detailed AMP rotation
  techniques that give competitive
  advantage in regenerative markets.
end note

== Sarah (regenerative producer) queries catalog ==

Sarah -> CF_EDC : DSP Catalog Query
note right of Sarah
  Token claims:
  membership: **active**
  participantType: **producer**
  certificationStatus: **regenerative-verified**
end note

group Access Policy: regenerative-producers
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : membership == "active" ? **YES**
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : participantType == "producer" ? **YES**
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : certificationStatus in\n["organic-certified",\n"regenerative-verified",\n"transitioning-organic"] ? **YES**
  note right of CF_EDC
    All 3 constraints pass.
    => Asset **VISIBLE** to Sarah
  end note
end

CF_EDC --> Sarah : Catalog includes proprietary\ngrazing protocol

|||

== Dr. Martinez (researcher) queries catalog ==

Martinez -> CF_EDC : DSP Catalog Query
note right of Martinez
  Token claims:
  membership: **active**
  participantType: **researcher**
  certificationStatus: **not-applicable**
end note

group Access Policy: regenerative-producers #FFEBEE
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : membership == "active" ? **YES**
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : participantType == "producer" ?\n"researcher" != "producer" => **NO**
  note right of CF_EDC #FFCDD2
    Failed at participantType check.
    => Asset **HIDDEN**
  end note
end

CF_EDC --> Martinez : Catalog does NOT include\nproprietary grazing protocol
note over Martinez
  Dr. Martinez doesn't see this asset.
  She can still access SOC measurements
  and other datasets with researchers-only
  or members-only access policies.
end note

|||

== Corporate Analyst queries catalog ==

Corp -> CF_EDC : DSP Catalog Query
note right of Corp
  Token claims:
  membership: **active**
  participantType: **corporate**
  certificationStatus: **not-applicable**
end note

group Access Policy: regenerative-producers #FFEBEE
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : membership == "active" ? **YES**
  CF_EDC -> CF_EDC : participantType == "producer" ?\n"corporate" != "producer" => **NO**
  note right of CF_EDC #FFCDD2
    => Asset **HIDDEN**
  end note
end

CF_EDC --> Corp : Catalog does NOT include\nproprietary grazing protocol

note over CF_EDC
  **Summary: Same asset, three different views**

  | Participant | Type | Cert. Status | Sees asset? |
  | Sarah | producer | regenerative | **Yes** |
  | Dr. Martinez | researcher | n/a | **No** |
  | Corp Analyst | corporate | n/a | **No** |

  The regenerative-producers policy creates a
  **trusted inner circle** among certified
  producers, protecting competitive
  practices from researchers and corporates.
end note

@enduml
